{"sectionId":651,"sectionIdLiteral":"651","humanId":"lesson-238","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"On my decision all salvation rests.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 238"},"annotation":"W-238","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-238\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"651#1\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"651#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Father, Your trust in me has been so great, I must be worthy.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"651#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>You created me, and know me as I am.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"651#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>And yet You placed Your Son‚Äôs salvation in my hands, and let it rest on my decision.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"651#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>I must be beloved of You indeed.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"651#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>And I must be steadfast in holiness as well, that You would give Your Son to me in certainty that he is safe Who still is part of You, and yet is mine, because He is my Self.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"651#2\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"651#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>And so, again today, we pause to think how much our Father loves us.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"651#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>And how dear His Son, created by His Love, remains to Him Whose Love is made complete in him.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"Father, Your trust in me has been so great, I must be worthy. You created me, and know me as I am. And yet You placed Your Son‚Äôs salvation in my hands, and let it rest on my decision. I must be","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 238: On my decision all salvation rests | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†238 ‚ÄúOn my decision all salvation rests‚Äù: Father, Your trust in me has been so gr